SQL: SELECT brand_name FROM aircraft_details WHERE registration = "N224CX";
actual_SQL:
SELECT brand_name
FROM aircraft_details
WHERE pure_reg = 'n224cx'
LIMIT 50;

SQL: SELECT brand_name FROM aircraft_details WHERE registration = "C-FSEP";
actual_SQL:
SELECT s.supplier_name
FROM aircraft_details a
JOIN supplier_details s ON a.supplier_id = s.supplier_id
WHERE a.pure_reg = 'cfsep'
LIMIT 50;
